This is my personnal configuration of emacs, you can use it, reuse it, abuse it.

1) create a public directory in ~/.emacs.d/

2) in "public" directory : git clone 

3) in ~/.emacs.d/init.el : (load "~/.emacs.d/public/activation.el)

Tree dir ~/.emacs.d :

~/.emacs.d/public
~/.emacs.d/prive
~/.emacs.d/init.el
etc.
